   Welcome to Collider-Accelerator TV on the Web

   This page brings you video pictures from the Collider-Accelerator Dept.

   You may choose from the two options on the left.

   Click on C-A TV to see the C-A Status screen that is on TV monitors in
   the C-A Dept. building.

   Click on PERFORMANCE to see the AGS Performance Monitor showing the AGS
   current transformer, main magnet current and spill.

   Click on the "Step" buttons to step through individual frames.

   Click on the "Push" button to have a stream of frames.

   Here's how it's done.

